<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>same again • same as ever</xh5><p> <i>same again—</i>used when ordering another drink of the same kind as the last: A thump on the counter brought the barmaid.... “<u>Same again</u>, ladies?”</p><p> <i>same as ever—</i>said of a person or thing not changed over a period of time: I have been perfectly charmed and overjoyed today, to find you just the <u>same as ever</u>.</p> </entry>
